description:
Watch as the story of the abduction of Dinah, Jacobs daughter, from Genesis Chapter 34 and Genesis Chapter 35 comes to life in iBIBLEthe worlds first visual and interactive Bible. Featured in the twenty-third chapter of iBIBLE is the story of Dinah, Jacobs daughter, who was taken by Shechem, a local rulers son, and forced himself on her. The sons of Jacob devised a plan and answered Shechem deceitfully when he asked for Dinah to be his wife. After all the men of Shechems city were circumcised, Levi and Simeon descended on the city. Study the Bible with your kids and enjoy the narrative presentation of Gods Word with iBIBLE.

A production of RevelationMedia, iBIBLE brings Gods Word to life in a format that people all over the world can engage with. Through dramatic audio and vibrant animation, people of all ages, all backgrounds, and with all abilities can learn the Biblical narrativethe one cohesive story of Scripture. iBIBLE will be available for free to translate into any of the worlds 7,000+ languages. Join the movement today and help bring the true story of Gods Word to the nations for free!

www.i.BIBLE

Director: Steve Cleary
